Class org.aimas.craftingquest.state.objects.Tower extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

Serialized Fields

remainingStrength

int remainingStrength
the remaining strength (expressed in energy points) of this tower

blueprint

Blueprint blueprint
the blueprint that was used to create this tower; it contains the resources required to build the tower and the amount of gold nuggets required for an upgrade to the next level

playerID

int playerID
the id of the player that built the tower

position

Point2i position
the tower's position on the map

sight

CellState[][] sight

The tower sight. It is a fixed (2 * towerRadius + 1) x (2 * towerRadius + 1) array of CellState objects.

The tower is positioned in the middle of the visibility array.

If the tower is near the margins of the map, cells falling outside the boundaries will be null.
